item.title: How I am making time for focus and creative thinking
item.description: If you have been in a meeting with me over the last month, you have likely been subject to one of my passionate pitches for you to try Delve Analytics. My passion is fueled by something very simple – it helped me. After 3 months, I feel more in control of my workday and better about the quality of my contributions. The amount of time I am spending “catching up” on weekends has decreased.
